WHAT IS MYTHAPPS?\n
MythApps is a wrapper that gives the illusion of Kodi plugins running natively from MythTV. Apps will comply with the Mythtv theming and remote commands.\n 
Kodi has a json API that allows remote control and to query the GUI. MythApps interprets this into its own GUI. Videos are played in the Kodi Video Player \n 
with some skinning tricks to make it feel like a native application.\n 
